\c 11
\s Sauro anokunda VaAmoni
\p
\v 1 Zvino Nahashi muAmoni wakakwira ndokuvaka musasa pakatarisana neJabheshi-Giriyadi. Zvino varume vose veJabheshi vakati kuna Nahashi: Ita sungano nesu, zvino tichakushumira.
\v 2 Nahashi muAmoni ndokuti kwavari: Ndichaita \add sungano\add* nemwi apa \add chete, \add*kuti nditumbure ziso renyu rose rerudyi, uye ndokuchiisa kuva chinyadzo pana Israeri wose.
\v 3 Zvino vakuru veJabheshi vakati kwaari: Tiregei mazuva manomwe kuti titume nhume kumuganhu wose waIsraeri; zvino kana pasina angatiponesa, tichabuda kuuya kwauri.
\p
\v 4 Zvino nhume dzikasvika paGibhiya raSauro, ndokutaura mashoko munzeve dzevanhu. Vanhu vose ndokusimudza inzwi ravo ndokuchema misodzi.
\v 5 Zvino tarira, Sauro wakauya shure kwenzombe kubva kumunda; Sauro ndokuti: Chii kuvanhu kuti vacheme? Zvino vakamuudza mashoko evarume veJabheshi.
\v 6 Zvino Mweya waMwari wakauya nesimba pamusoro paSauro paakanzwa mashoko awa; hasha dzake ndokupfuta zvikuru.
\v 7 Zvino wakatora nzombe mbiri, ndokudzigura kuita nhindi, ndokutumira kumuganhu wose waIsraeri neruoko rwenhume achiti: Ani nani asingabudi kutevera Sauro nekutevera Samueri, zvichaitwa saizvozvo kunzombe dzake. Zvino kutya Jehovha kwakawira pavanhu, zvino vakabuda semunhu umwe.
\v 8 Paaivaverenga paBhezeki, vana vaIsraeri vakava zvuru mazana matatu, uye varume vaJudha zvuru makumi matatu.
\v 9 Zvino vakati kunhume dzakauya: Muchaudza varume veJabheshi-Giriyadi seizvi: Mangwana zuva ropisa muchava neruponeso. Pakasvika nhume ndokuudza varume veJabheshi, ivo vakafara.
\v 10 Naizvozvo varume veJabheshi vakati: Mangwana tichabuda kwamuri, mutiitire zvinoenderana nezvose zvakanaka pameso enyu.
\v 11 Zvino zvakaitika chifume kuti Sauro wakaisa vanhu mumapoka matatu; ivo ndokupinda pakati pemusasa pamurindiro wemangwanani, ndokuuraya VaAmoni kusvika pakupisa kwezuva. Zvino zvakaitika kuti avo vakasara vakapararira, uye hakuna kusiiwa kwavari vaviri vari pamwe.
\p
\v 12 Zvino vanhu vakati kuna Samueri: Ndiani wakati: Sauro achatonga here pamusoro pedu? Ipai varume avo, tivauraye.
\v 13 Sauro ndokuti: Hakungaurawi munhu zuva rino, nokuti nhasi Jehovha waita ruponeso kwaIsraeri.
\v 14 Zvino Samueri wakati kuvanhu: Uyai tiende kuGirigari, tinovandudza umambo ipapo.
\v 15 Vanhu vose ndokuenda kuGirigari, vakaita Sauro ave mambo pamberi paJehovha paGirigari. Zvino ipapo vakabaira zvibairo zvezvipo zvekuyananisa pamberi paJehovha; ipapo Sauro nevarume vose vaIsraeri vakafara zvikuru kwazvo.